title: Munch Madness: Subway vs Arby's with Jen D'Angelo (w/ Deli Boys as Pickle Correspondents)
itunes:title: Munch Madness: Subway vs Arby's with Jen D'Angelo (w/ Deli Boys as Pickle Correspondents)
description:
Jen D’Angelo (Solar Opposites, Young Rock) joins the 'boys to talk about Key West before tackling the semi-soft finals of Munch Madness 2022: The Tournament of Chompions: Hero's Journey: Sub-Optimal. Plus, the Deli Boys weigh in as Pickle Correspondents.
